Package: covid19india
Type: Package
Title: Pulling clean data from covid10india.org
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Max", "Salvatore", email = "mmsalva@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package was designed while working with data on COVID-19 in India. covid19india.org is 
    a data resource with APIs available. It is updated daily and provides count, testing, and vaccine data 
    at the national, state, and district level. This package eases the process for R users to obtain data 
    ready for analysis in hopes of ddemocratizing data science and speed up public health research.
